OpenEmbedded/Yocto BSP Layer for Host Mobility products

This layer adds our custom machine configurations that include u-boot, drivers and Linux kernels. 
It supports poky v4 (kirkstone).

=====================================================================

This layer provides support for:

- MX-4 C61 (mx4-c61)
- MX-4 T30 (mx4-t30) (both T30 and T30FR)
- MX-V PT (mx5-pt)
- HMX (soon to be introduced)

For more information on available Host Moblity products please visit:

https://hostmobility.com

Maintainer
=======

This layer is maintained by Host Mobility AB.

